# Authentication 

**Token Creation**

The call requires a Bearer token to be sent in the HTTP Authorization header.  This token can be generated by signing into your staging, sandbox, or production environment, selecting User Settings > API Keys and Add API Key.

![alt text](./images/token.png)

**Authentication**

For all API calls, you need to provide an HTTP Authorization header.  The value of this header should be your API Key preceded by the word ‘Bearer’

e.g. Authorization: Bearer eyJoXE232wZe34rkjkr….

You can retrieve your API key on your profile settings page.

